'''安妮塔·博格婦女與科技研究所'''是由[[美國|美國]]計算機科學家[[安妮塔·博格|安妮塔·博格]]创建的一个 [[非营利组织#United_States|非营利组织]]。这组织最主要最显著的计划是全球最大计算机领域里的女性大会-葛麗絲·霍普女性計算科學大会。<ref name="ghcreg11">{{cite web|title=Registration Now Open for the 2011 Grace Hopper Celebration of Women in Computing|url=http://gracehopper.org/2011/news/registration-now-open-for-the-2011-grace-hopper-celebration-of-women-in-computing|work=gracehopper.org|publisher=Anita Borg Institute for Women and Technology|accessdate=27 June 2011|date=7 June 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110612183413/http://gracehopper.org/2011/news/registration-now-open-for-the-2011-grace-hopper-celebration-of-women-in-computing/|archivedate=2011年6月12日}}</ref> 基于加利福尼亚州[[帕洛阿尔托|帕洛阿尔托]]，安妮塔·博格婦女與科技研究所目前由[[Telle_Whitney|Telle Whitney]]所领导,她和安妮塔·博格共同创建了葛麗絲·霍普女性計算科學大会。<ref>{{cite web|last=Anderson|first=Melissa|title=Telle Whitney, CEO and President, Anita Borg Institute for Women and Technology|url=http://www.theglasshammer.com/news/2011/05/11/voice-of-experience-telle-whitney-ceo-and-president-anita-borg-institute-for-women-and-technology|work=The Glass Hammer|publisher=Evolved People Media LLC|accessdate=27 June 2011|date=11 May 2011|archive-date=2011-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110515174947/http://www.theglasshammer.com/news/2011/05/11/voice-of-experience-telle-whitney-ceo-and-president-anita-borg-institute-for-women-and-technology/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==伙伴公司==
安妮塔·博格研究所在科技圈内外得到一些伙伴公司的支持。现有伙伴包括: [[Google|Google]],[[HP|HP]], [[Microsoft|Microsoft]], [[CA_Technologies|CA Technologies]], [[Cisco|Cisco]], [[Facebook|Facebook]],[[First_Republic_Bank|First Republic Bank]], [[IBM|IBM]], [[Intel|Intel]], [[Intuit|Intuit]], [[Lockheed_Martin|Lockheed Martin]], [[National_Science_Foundation|National Science Foundation]], [[National_Security_Agency|National Security Agency]],[[NetApp|NetApp]], [[SAP_AG|SAP]], [[Symantec|Symantec]], [[Thomson_Reuters|Thomson Reuters]], [[Wilson_Sonsini_Goodrich_&_Rosati|Wilson Sonsini Goodrich & Rosati]], [[Amazon.com|Amazon]], [[Broadcom|Broadcom]],[[Motorola|Motorola Foundation]], [[Raytheon|Raytheon]], [[Salesforce|Salesforce]], and[[Yahoo!|Yahoo!]] 。<ref>{{cite web|title=About Us: ABI Partners|url=http://anitaborg.org/about/abi-partners|publisher=Anita Borg Institute for Women and Technology|accessdate=24 June 2011|date=14 June 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110710032814/http://anitaborg.org/about/abi-partners/|archivedate=2011年7月10日}}</ref>

